      "playtime_at_review": 12809,
      "review_text": "If you are a person who generates dopamine by pressing the same button for 5 minutes, this is your game. Wanna win a game, pick the huge hitbox signatures with fast speed and there you go, you have just became a bot. It would be a relief that the dead internet theory applies to this community, because I can't express how much toxic and dumb are most of the players in gold and plat. If you wanna play a character that doesn't have good weapons or signatures, either you spend 5k hours in that same character, or you just lose again and again. \nJust to mention that more than 90% of my games are with Kor (a character of the game), and I play better almost every other character with any other weapon. Please, leave the game while you can.\nEdit: Played again after some patches to see if there was hope. I still don't understand how the idea of balance of the brawlhalla developers is so different compared to other games. Gonna take another time and hope they look at their community's feedback and actually make decisions based on it.",
      "timestamp_created": 1758488866
    },
    {
      "review_id": "221321900",
      "author_steamid": "76561199164399180",
      "voted_up": true,
      "votes_up": 0,
      "playtime_at_review": 9340,
      "review_text": "With someone who has been diamond multiple seasons since the game came out with over 1000 hours on xbox and climbing on pc, I conclude that if brawlhalla was indeed a woman I would marry her. A lot of people who suck and have a skill issue have a problem with the new movement but don’t listen to them I highly recommend brawlhalla, come be apart of the cult😁",
      "timestamp_created": 1774131742
    },
